6. Commit Phase
	â€¢	Once work is ready, React commits updates:
	â€¢	Applies changes to the real DOM.
	â€¢	Runs useLayoutEffect (before paint).
	â€¢	Runs useEffect (after paint).
	â€¢	Important: Commit phase is always synchronous.

